        <td><span data-conref="Tag_optional.hts"> </span> The offset, or starting index, in the array. Setting a negative value will count from the end of the array. The starting index will then be <span class="inline2">array_length(array) + offset</span>. See: <a data-xref="{text}" href="../../GameMaker_Language/GML_Reference/Variable_Functions/Array_Functions.htm#h1">Offset And Length</a></td>
