        <td><span data-conref="Tag_optional.hts"> </span> The number of elements to traverse. A negative value will traverse the array backwards (i.e. in descending order of indices, e.g. 2, 1, 0 instead of 2, 3, 4). See: <a data-xref="{text}" href="../../GameMaker_Language/GML_Reference/Variable_Functions/Array_Functions.htm#h1">Offset And Length</a></td>
